    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Deed books, 1761-1769, of Amherst County Court. The deed books record the name of the grantor and grantee, the residence of both individuals and the description of property being sold or transferred. Both
volumes have indexes which contains the first and last names of both parties. It is arranged alphabetically from A-Z.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
